हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा।

show.description: 'Rebirth: Hunting Crimes Album' tells the story of a girl, a former assassin reborn with supernatural abilities and a new life as a teenager. She faces accusations of murder and hacking, but her unique skills attract the attention of a military officer, leading to a proposition of marriage in exchange for clearing her name. The narrative explores themes of revenge, redemption, and the complexities of navigating a new life with a dark past.
